\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {7.6}{\ignorespaces Layer-wise evolution of language representations in Llama-3.2-1B. Clusters emerge loosely in early layers (a), sharpen in middle layers (b), and reach near-perfect separability in final layers. The explained variance of the first principal component (c) increases dramatically in final layers, confirming late-stage specialization for language identity.}}{31}{figure.caption.34}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:layer_evolution}{{7.6}{31}{Layer-wise evolution of language representations in Llama-3.2-1B. Clusters emerge loosely in early layers (a), sharpen in middle layers (b), and reach near-perfect separability in final layers. The explained variance of the first principal component (c) increases dramatically in final layers, confirming late-stage specialization for language identity}{figure.caption.34}{}}
